{\pard\plain\s0 The best a fatalistic psychology can do is poison you with false medicines. In fact...I would say that the psychologists are the Fatalist Priesthood of Pharmakeia. Most people are dishonest and afraid. And the honest ones are often mean. \par}
{\pard\plain\s0 So life is pretty grim. Especially if we\rquote re just libido eating bugs.\par}
