{\pard\plain\s0 The State appropriates the Human admiration for the Hero, cynically inspiring him to compromise himself on the ambitious altars of evil men conspiring to outwit the still more evil.\par}
{\pard\plain\s0\par}
{\pard\plain\s0 They don\rquote t want you to recognize classical pronouns so that classical literature becomes distasteful to you. And Classical literature is of a Higher Sort. I still remember a time when that fact was commonly known. A time when people reverenced virtue.\par}
