{\pard\plain\s0 While others learn to become more machine-like, I learn to grow more human. Humans are free. Machines receive instructions. The NPCs receiving subliminal instructions by the power of push notification (power of suggestion), would prefer not to be awakened to their sorry spiritual state. They do not have eyes to see. They do not have ears to hear. I have to tell them. Because for some reason, I remember.\par}
